snippet.title: Dungeon Rushers - Launch trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the official gameplay launch trailer for Dungeon Rushers, available worldwide on Tuesday, September 6th on Steam. 

Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/429620
Official Website: http://dungeon-rushers.com
Facebook: https://facebook.com/dungeonrushers
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/dungeonrushers

Concept & prod: Johann Verbroucht (@jverbroucht)
Animations: Victor Nardin (@VNardin)
Voice & Sounds: Oscar Garvin: https://soundcloud.com/oscastyle
Musics: Robin Dussart = https://soundcloud.com/robindussart
Artworks: Thomas Frick @ThomasFrick
